            "secId": "sec2.1",
            "sentence": "Given a continuous finite element space, based on at least second order polynomials for the plate, we define the finite element space for the one\u2013dimensional structure as the restriction of the plate finite element space to the structure which is geometrically modeled by an embedded curve or line.",
            "startOffset": 113261,
