                    "endOffset": 123608,
                    "startOffset": 123607
                }
            },
            "secId": "sec3.2",
            "sentence": "Other boundary conditions for plates, for instance simply supported and free, can easily be included in the c/dG finite element method, see Ref. [8] for details.",
