                    "startOffset": 114653
                }
            },
            "secId": "sec2.1",
            "sentence": "The work presented here is an extension of earlier work [4] where membrane structures were considered, in which case a linear approximation in the bulk suffices.",
            "startOffset": 114596,
            "title": "The basic approach"
        },
        {
