            "title": "The Euler\u2013Bernoulli beam model"
        },
        {
            "endOffset": 111768,
            "parents": [],
            "secId": "sec1",
            "sentence": "The important issue is how to couple the variables of the beam to the variables of the plate.",
            "startOffset": 111675,
            "title": "Introduction"
        },
        {
            "endOffset": 132470,
            "parents": [],
            "secId": "sec5",
            "sentence": "We have formulated a continuous/discontinuous Galerkin method for beam reinforced thin plates.",
